- poll_write: cancel-safe (partial write OK)
- write_all: NOT cancel-safe (partial state)
- WritePermit: cancel-safe (uncommitted data dropped)
- flush: cancel-safe (can retry)
- shutdown: cancel-safe (idempotent)

